<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bread Financial Case Study - Annie Sommer</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
   <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,200..800;1,6..72,200..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
   			 --primary-color: #334EAC; /* Royal */
   			 --secondary-color: #081F5C; /* Midnight */
   			 --accent-color: #7096D1; /* China */
  			--text-color: #334EAC; /* Royal for main text */
  			--text-secondary: #7096D1; /* China for secondary text */
   			 --text-muted: #BAD6EB; /* Sky for muted text */
   			 --light-gray: #F7F2EB; /* Moon */
   			 --border-color: #EDF1F6; /* Porcelain */
   			 --background-accent: #D0E3FF; /* Dawn */
            --sidebar-width: 240px; 
            --base-font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
        }
        
        .container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            gap: 3rem;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        /* Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            width: var(--sidebar-width);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 2rem;
            height: fit-content;
        }
        
        .back-link {
            color: #7096D1
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .back-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        
        
        .toc {
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .toc h3 {
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .toc ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .toc li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .toc a {
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .toc a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color: rgba(247, 242, 235, 0.25);
            padding-left: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Active TOC link styling */
        .toc a.active {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color:	rgba(247, 242, 235, 0.45);
            padding-left: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
        }
        /* Smooth transition for TOC links */
        .toc a {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 3px solid transparent;
        }
        
        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
            max-width: 760px;
        }
        
        .project-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .project-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .project-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7096D1;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .project-summary {
            font-size: .9rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .content-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h3 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        .content-section p {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .content-section ul, .content-section ol {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
        }
        
        .content-section li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box p, .highlight-box ul {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7096D1;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .image-placeholder {
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #7096D1;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Thumbnail styling */
        .thumbnail {
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .thumbnail:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .thumbnail img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .thumbnail:hover img {
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        /* Fullscreen modal */
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1000;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal.active {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .modal-content {
            max-width: 90vw;
            max-height: 80vh;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .modal-caption {
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .modal-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
        }

        .modal-close:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        .navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 1rem;
                gap: 2rem;
            }
            
            .sidebar {
                width: 100%;
                position: static;
                order: 2;
            }
            
            .main-content {
                order: 1;
            }
            
            .project-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .project-meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }

            /* Mobile responsive for modal */
            .modal-content {
                max-width: 95vw;
                max-height: 70vh;
            }
            
            .modal-close {
                top: 1rem;
                right: 1rem;
                width: 35px;
                height: 35px;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .modal-caption {
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Sidebar with TOC -->
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← home </a>
            <nav class="toc">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#problem">User Problem</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#strategy">Strategy</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#solution">Solution</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#design">Design</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#results">Results</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </aside>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="main-content">
            <header class="project-header">
                <h1>Bread Financial Mobile App</h1>
                
                <div class="project-meta">
                    <span><strong>Role:</strong>UX/UI Designer</span>
                    <span><strong>Client:</strong> https://www.breadfinancial.com/</span>
                    <span><strong>Agency:</strong> Razorfish</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-summary">
                <p>Strategy, UX/UI on a credit card app for a value-focused Fintech </p> </div>
            </header>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="problem">
                <h2>User Problem</h2>
                <p>
                    Bread financial users needed an easy way to view their card, pay their bill, and manage their accounts. 
                </p>
                            
                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="Bread was in need of a fresh, friendly UI and straightforward practical features">
                        <img src="/img/Bread/onboarding.jpg" alt="onboarding flow for Bread financial">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="strategy">
                <h2>Strategy</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Research:</strong> I inherited research from the great usability teams at Sapient-Razorfish on usescases and user preferences </li>
                    <li><strong>Wireframed:</strong> I was responsible for wifreframing every workflow for the app over the Christmas break so that the teams could come back and have something to work from </li>
                    <li><strong>Design:</strong> Once the wireframes were shipped, I worked with the rest of the team to split off and design features and add UI </li>
                    <li><strong>Ship:</strong>We shipped MVP features for both apps over around 1.5 quarters</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>My Role & Contribution</h3>
                <p>I was hired in just before christmas break and did a two week wireframing/user journey sprint alone, digesting research and requirements and churning out Figma frames, on all MVP flows to be waiting for everyone to pounce on when they got back.</p>
                <p>After that, I pitched strategy, developed UX flows, annotated UIs and wrote suggested copy</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="solution">
                <h2>Solution</h2>
                <p>Our target users skewed younger, so we oriented the app vertically and kept the brand front and center</p>

                <p>We kept the UI round, lightweight, and minimalist. The copy voice, which often originated with my user journeys and persisted, was friendly.</p>
                
                <p>We always kept the user grounded in narrative scenarios when mapping screens. This allowed for constant iteration based on situational and user context. </p>

                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="Figjam I created that digested research and branding documentation and some business requirements.">
                        <img src="/img/Bread/cardlockflow.jpg" alt="wireframes Bread financial app">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="content-section" id="design">
                <h2>Design</h2>
                <p>We used my wireframes and brand design artifacts to establish a look and feel for the elements of the app. We put those together in more rudimentary, annotated workflows to then polish into full mocks to send to ENG. </p>            
                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="High fidelity wireframe using UI elements and annotations">
                        <img src="/img/Bread/highfidelitywire.jpg" alt="Shark robot vacuum VUI flow diagram">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p>II helped define the look fo the UI, building out and pitching elements for the design system that were ultimately accepted. I built the card lock/unlock workflows in settings and shipped this feature from UX --> UI --> Delivery. </p>          
                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="Card lock/unlock workflow">
                        <img src="/img/Bread/cardlockunlock.jpg" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
              </section>
            <section class="content-section" id="results">
                <h2>Results</h2>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">89k</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Ratings on the app store </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">4.8★</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">App store rating</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h2>Insights</h2>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Process doesn't have to be perfect to work</h3>
                    <p>Doing a heads-down grind to wire out the entire app while everyone was away on christmas break was an unconventional approach for razorfish, but it paid off immensely in delivery efficiencies</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Designing for finance requires narrative awareness</h3>
                    <p>In financial app designs, dollar-data is always high stakes and abundant. But the narrative behind every number matters more than the number itself. </p>
                </div> 
            </section>
            
